description:
MetadataExtractor is a straightforward and lightweight library for reading metadata from image and video files.
      It reads Exif, IPTC, XMP, ICC, Photoshop, WebP, PNG, BMP, GIF, ICO, PCX metadata from JPEG, TIFF WebP, PSD, PNG, BMP, GIF, ICO, PCX and camera RAW files.
      Camera manufacturer specific support exists for Agfa, Canon, Casio, Epson, Fujifilm, Kodak, Kyocera, Leica, Minolta, Nikon, Olympus, Panasonic, Pentax, Reconyx, Sanyo, Sigma/Foveon and Sony models.
      In addition, MOV and related QuickTime video formats are supported such as MP4, M4V, 3G2, 3GP.

      This package supports:

      - .NET Framework 3.5
      - .NET Framework 4.5
      - Silverlight 5.0
      - Windows 8.0
      - Windows Phone 8.1
      - Windows Phone Silverlight 8.0
summary: A straightforward library for reading metadata from image and video files.

It does NOT contain code to parse .ogg or .opus container files or to manage RTP packet streams. Support for reading/writing .opus files can be found in the Concentus.OggFile package
